530
00:44:03,720 --> 00:44:06,390
Then so be it, idiot!

531
00:44:06,390 --> 00:44:08,930
Why are you so angry?

532
00:44:08,930 --> 00:44:11,880
When you suddenly stop responding,

533
00:44:11,880 --> 00:44:14,380
so I assume you've lost consciousness.

534
00:44:14,380 --> 00:44:17,530
But you just fell asleep...

535
00:44:17,530 --> 00:44:19,950
Sorry. I've been a little sleep-deprived.

536
00:44:19,950 --> 00:44:23,590
And your head injury only needed two stitches.

537
00:44:23,590 --> 00:44:25,480
What? Only two?

538
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:29,470
