541
00:44:41,220 --> 00:44:45,860
But... didn't you say something in the ambulance?

542
00:44:46,490 --> 00:44:51,830
"If you get through this, I'll grant any wish you want."

543
00:44:54,240 --> 00:44:56,250
It must have been your imagination.

544
00:44:56,250 --> 00:44:59,780
You definitely said it.

545
00:45:00,650 --> 00:45:02,470
Probably...

546
00:45:03,270 --> 00:45:10,170
