547
00:45:13,070 --> 00:45:16,520
I'm starting to remember!

548
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:20,200
You said you would kiss me! Go on a date! Anything!

549
00:45:24,740 --> 00:45:28,520
You have to keep the promise!

550
00:45:29,620 --> 00:45:34,730
As I said, I didn't promise you anything.

551
00:45:34,730 --> 00:45:39,910
Doctor! A Japanese man never goes back on his word, right?

552
00:45:39,910 --> 00:45:43,470
♫ The world has changed since you came in ♫

553
00:45:43,470 --> 00:45:48,930
♫ In the midst of my flawless days, ♫

554
00:45:49,740 --> 00:45:51,530
You idiot.

555
00:45:54,290 --> 00:45:57,080
Did I really imagine it?

556
00:45:57,080 --> 00:46:00,270
Must be because I hit my head...

557
00:46:00,270 --> 00:46:07,620
♫ I love, I love, so many times ♫

558
00:46:07,620 --> 00:46:14,550
♫ In the midst of growing love and changing emotions ♫

559
00:46:14,550 --> 00:46:19,440
♫ You shine brightly ♫

560
00:46:19,450 --> 00:46:27,090
♫ Like paints diving into a water tank and melting ♫

561
00:46:27,090 --> 00:46:29,460
This is part of your treatment.

562
00:46:30,130 --> 00:46:36,990
♫ I wouldn't have noticed such vivid colors ♫

